    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Reserved volume name /opt/liferay/data for Liferay and Backup services. Click <a href=\"/w/api-update-release-announcement\" target=\"_self\">here</a> for more information.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed misspelling error for LIFERAY_CLUSTER_PERIOR_LINK_PERIOD_AUTODETECT_PERIOD_ADDRESS</li>\n<li>Fixed Database instances ids and reserved volumes should last through service deletion</li>\n<li>Fixed Freshly deployed database, liferay, or backup service does not have database instance id environment variables</li>\n<li>Fixed Backup deployment fails due to missing PVC</li>\n</ul>"
      },
